5).
<p id="my"  onmouseover="change()" onmouseout="restore()"> js is used to make a web dynamically use of web for the user </p>

<script>
function change() {
    document.getElementById("my").style.color = "yellow";
}

function restore() {
    document.getElementById("my").style.color = "black";

}
</script>
